{"tid":1027230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國首相發言人：仍在評估5G風險　尚未就華為作出決定","createTime":"2019-02-18T16:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T18:20:39.000Z","uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23a0ee402aa49cf17e8253750773572597a0b2ec","tid":1027230,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>英國正評估5G風險 華為前途未定案</strong><br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》稍早引述兩名知情人士報道，英國政府已達成結論，認為當局有能力採取措施，緩解由於使用中國華為5G電訊設備所帶來的安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相文翠珊發言人James Slack表示，仍在繼續評估5G安全和韌性的正確的政策方法，由於評估涉及一系列的選項，尚未就華為作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2061505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2061505&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEgQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=a05a294b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2061505</a>"},{"pid":"b0090d38a989aaf97c4a48a0bb988a10c965d64f","tid":1027230,"uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》稍早引述兩名知情人士報道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又撚狗"},{"pid":"8861250500a9fe214a56788b1c7e58deac26f8b3","tid":1027230,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋4g 同5g嘅分野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f39ce52aa27ef6fe96e4c006077502158822203","tid":1027230,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0090d38a989aaf97c4a48a0bb988a10c965d64f","tid":1027230,"uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》稍早引述兩名知情人士報道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又撚狗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:38:57.000Z",